      "source": [
        "## Data loading\n",
        "\n",
        "Default path:\n",
        "\n",
        "- `data_source='huggingface'` loads `Lichess/chess-openings`\n",
        "\n",
        "Optional alternatives:\n",
        "\n",
        "- `data_source='kaggle_csv'` loads a CSV export of the same openings dataset\n",
        "- `data_source='pgn_file'` parses a raw Lichess PGN file and uses `ECO` / `Opening` headers as task labels\n"
      ]
    },
